Example point locations

vancouver_points.Rd

Shapefile with point locations North Vancouver, BC, Canada. To use this data set, you need to terra::unwrap it first, e.g.: vancouver_points <- terra::unwrap(get(data(vancouver_points)))

Usage

vancouver_points

Format

PackedSpatVector

Source

derived from dem_vancouver
